d','Shipping to' => 'Cludo i','Shipping method' => 'Dull cludo','Additional notes' => 'Nodiadau ychwanegol','Billing to' => 'Bilio i','Payment method' => 'Dull talu','Step %1$s of %2$s' => 'Cam %1$s o %2$s','Change: %s' => 'Newid: %s','An account will be created with the information provided.' => 'Bydd cyfrif yn cael ei greu gyda&#39;r wybodaeth a ddarperir.','Not selected yet.' => 'Heb ei ddewis eto.','Same as shipping address' => 'Yr un peth â&#39;r cyfeiriad cludo','Same as billing address' => 'Yr un peth â&#39;r cyfeiriad bilio','Order summary' => 'Crynodeb archeb','Edit cart' => 'Golygu cart','Did you mean %s?' => 'Oeddech chi&#39;n golygu %s?','Change email address to: {suggestion-value}' => 'Newid cyfeiriad e-bost i: {suggestion-value}','This is a required field.' => 'Mae hwn yn faes gofynnol.','This is not a valid email address.' => 'Nid yw hwn yn gyfeiriad e-bost dilys.','This field does not match the related field value.' => 'Nid yw&#39;r maes hwn yn cyfateb i&#39;r gwerth maes cysylltiedig.','The CPF number "{cpf_number}" is invalid.' => 'Mae&#39;r rhif CPF &quot;{cpf_number}&quot; yn annilys.','The CNPJ number "{cnpj_number}" is invalid.' => 'Mae&#39;r rhif CNPJ &quot;{cnpj_number}&quot; yn annilys.','(Required)' => '(Angenrheidiol)','Checkout Header - Desktop' => 'Pennawd Desg dalu - Bwrdd Gwaith','Display widgets on the checkout header for large screens. Only displayed if using the plugin\'s checkout header.' => 'Arddangos teclynnau ar bennyn y ddesg dalu ar gyfer sgriniau mawr. Dim ond os ydych chi&#39;n defnyddio pennyn til yr ategyn y caiff ei ddangos.','Checkout Header - Mobile' => 'Pennawd Desg dalu - Symudol','Display widgets below the checkout header for mobile devices. Only displayed if using the plugin\'s checkout header.' => 'Arddangos teclynnau o dan bennawd y ddesg dalu ar gyfer dyfeisiau symudol. Dim ond os ydych chi&#39;n defnyddio pennyn til yr ategyn y caiff ei ddangos.','Checkout Sidebar' => 'Bar Ochr Talu','Display widgets on the checkout sidebar after the order summary.' => 'Arddangos teclynnau ar y bar ochr desg dalu ar ôl y crynodeb archeb.','Checkout Order Summary' => 'Crynodeb Gorchymyn Talu','Display widgets inside the order summary at the checkout page.' => 'Arddangos teclynnau y tu mewn i&#39;r crynodeb archeb ar y dudalen ddesg dalu.','Checkout Below Place Order' => 'Desg Dalu Islaw Archeb Lle','Display widgets below the place order button at the checkout page.' => 'Arddangos teclynnau o dan y botwm archebu lle ar y dudalen ddesg dalu.','Checkout Footer' => 'Troedyn desg dalu','Display widgets on the checkout footer. Only displayed if using the plugin\'s checkout footer.' => 'Arddangos teclynnau ar droedyn y ddesg dalu. Dim ond os ydych chi&#39;n defnyddio troedyn til yr ategyn y caiff ei ddangos.','Classic' => 'Clasurol','Boxed' => 'Mewn bocsio','Split' => 'Hollti','Minimalist' => 'Minimalaidd','Fluid Checkout and Delivery Date plugins by CodeRockz' => 'Ategion Talu Hylif a Dyddiad Cyflenwi gan CodeRockz','<p>We detected that you are using the plugins Delivery & Pickup Date Time for WooCommerce (free and PRO) by CodeRockz. Integration with these plugins have been moved to Fluid Checkout PRO.</p>' => '<p>Rydym wedi canfod eich bod yn defnyddio&#39;r ategion Amser Dyddiad Cyflenwi a Chodi ar gyfer WooCommerce (am ddim a PRO) gan CodeRockz. Mae integreiddio gyda&#39;r ategion hyn wedi&#39;u symud i Fluid Checkout PRO.</p>','Upgrade to PRO' => 'Uwchraddio i PRO','Fluid Checkout database updated successfully' => 'Diweddarwyd cronfa ddata Hylif Checkout yn llwyddiannus','The database changes where applied successfully.' => 'Mae&#39;r gronfa ddata yn newid lle cymhwysir yn llwyddiannus.','Ok' => 'Iawn','Dismiss' => 'Diystyru','Fluid Checkout database update' => 'Diweddariad cronfa ddata Hylif Checkout','Some changes to the database are required. As with any update, we recommend you to <strong>take a full backup of your website before proceeding</strong>.' => 'Mae angen rhai newidiadau i&#39;r gronfa ddata. Fel gydag unrhyw ddiweddariad, rydym yn argymell eich bod yn <strong>gwneud copi wrth gefn llawn o&#39;ch gwefan cyn symud ymlaen</strong> .','Update database' => 'Diweddaru cronfa ddata','Fluid Checkout is not compatible with the Divi Builder checkout layout' => 'Nid yw Hylif Desg yn gydnaws â chynllun desg dalu Divi Builder','<p>Fluid Checkout needs the classic WooCommerce shortcode-based checkout form to work. When using the Divi Builder to customize the look and feel of the checkout page, the classic shortcodes are replaced with custom widgets from the Divi Builder for each part of the checkout page. These custom widgets are not compatible with Fluid Checkout.</p><p>Please edit your checkout page replacing the Divi Builder widgets with the a text widget containing the shortcode <code>[woocommerce_checkout]</code>.</p>' => '<p>Mae angen y ffurflen ddesg dalu glasurol ar sail cod byr WooCommerce i weithio. Wrth ddefnyddio Divi Builder i addasu edrychiad a theimlad y dudalen ddesg dalu, mae&#39;r codau byr clasurol yn cael eu disodli gan widgets personol o&#39;r Divi Builder ar gyfer pob rhan o&#39;r dudalen ddesg dalu. Nid yw&#39;r teclynnau personol hyn yn gydnaws â Hylif Desg.</p><p> Golygwch eich tudalen ddesg dalu gan ddisodli&#39;r teclynnau Divi Builder gyda&#39;r teclyn testun sy&#39;n cynnwys y cod byr <code>[woocommerce_checkout]</code> .</p>','Edit the checkout page' => 'Golygu&#39;r dudalen ddesg dalu','Read the documentation.' => 'Darllenwch y ddogfennaeth.','Germanized PRO multistep checkout feature needs to be disabled when using Fluid Checkout' => 'Mae angen analluogi nodwedd desg dalu aml-gam PRO Almaeneg wrth ddefnyddio Hylif Desg','When using Fluid Checkout, the multistep feature from the Germanized PRO plugin becomes unnecessary and can cause <strong>critical errors while processing new orders</strong>. Please disable the Germanized PRO multistep checkout feature in the plugin settings.' => 'Wrth ddefnyddio Fluid Checkout, mae&#39;r nodwedd aml-gam o&#39;r ategyn Germanized PRO yn dod yn ddiangen a gall achosi <strong>gwallau critigol wrth brosesu archebion newydd</strong> . Analluoga&#39;r nodwedd til aml-gam PRO Almaenegedig yng ngosodiadau&#39;r ategyn.','Go to Germanized settings' => 'Ewch i osodiadau Almaeneg','Thanks for choosing Fluid Checkout!' => 'Diolch am ddewis Hylif Checkout!','You have been using the plugin for a while now. How do you like it so far? <br>Please give us a quick rating, we appreciate every bit of feedback and it encourages us to keep improving the plugin :)' => 'Rydych chi wedi bod yn defnyddio&#39;r ategyn ers tro bellach. Sut ydych chi&#39;n ei hoffi hyd yn hyn?<br> Rhowch sgôr cyflym i ni, rydym yn gwerthfawrogi pob tamaid o adborth ac mae&#39;n ein hannog i barhau i wella&#39;r ategyn :)','Rate the plugin' => 'Graddiwch yr ategyn','I need help!' => 'Dwi angen help!','The plugin WooCommerce Checkout Manager by Quadlayers is not compatibile with Fluid Checkout' => 'Nid yw&#39;r ategyn WooCommerce Checkout Manager gan Quadlayers yn gydnaws â Hylif Checkout','Some features of WooCommerce Checkout Manager by Quadlayers might not work as expected when using it with Fluid Checkout. Read <a href="%s">our documentation</a> for more information and alternative solutions.' => 'Efallai na fydd rhai nodweddion o WooCommerce Checkout Manager gan Quadlayers yn gweithio yn ôl y disgwyl wrth ei ddefnyddio gyda Fluid Checkout. Darllenwch <a href="%s">ein dogfennaeth</a> am ragor o wybodaeth ac atebion amgen.','Read documentation' => 'Darllen dogfennaeth','Don\'t show this again' => 'Peidiwch â dangos hyn eto','Special offers' => 'Cynigion arbennig','Extend all the goodness of Fluid Checkout to your cart page and thank you pages.' => 'Ymestyn holl ddaioni Hylif Desg i&#39;ch tudalen cart a&#39;ch tudalennau diolch.','Fluid Checkout PRO' => 'Hylif Checkout PRO','Design templates, optimized cart and order received pages, account matching, and much more.' => 'Dylunio templedi, tudalennau wedi&#39;u optimeiddio ar gyfer cert a archeb, paru cyfrifon, a llawer mwy.','The best tools to further <strong>improve your WooCommerce checkout conversion rate</strong> and make the purchase experience consistent on the entire journey.' => 'Yr offer gorau i <strong>wella&#39;ch cyfradd trosi til WooCommerce</strong> ymhellach a gwneud y profiad prynu yn gyson ar y daith gyfan.','More design templates' => 'Mwy o dempledi dylunio','Optimized cart page' => 'Tudalen cart wedi&#39;i optimeiddio','Optimized order received / thank you page' => 'Gorchymyn wedi&#39;i optimeiddio wedi&#39;i dderbyn / tudalen diolch','Edit cart contents at checkout page' => 'Golygu cynnwys y drol ar y dudalen ddesg dalu','Account matching / user matching' => 'Paru cyfrif / paru defnyddwyr','Express Checkout buttons from supported payment methods' => 'Botymau Talu Cyflym o ddulliau talu â chymorth','Trust symbols on the cart and thank you pages' => 'Ymddiriedwch symbolau ar y drol a thudalennau diolch','More positions for the coupon code on the checkout page' => 'Mwy o swyddi ar gyfer y cod cwpon ar y dudalen ddesg dalu','Integrated coupon code field on the cart page' => 'Maes cod cwpon integredig ar dudalen y drol','International phone numbers' => 'Rhifau ffôn rhyngwladol','Gift messages and packing slips' => 'Negeseuon rhodd a slipiau pacio','Local pickup and in-store collection' => 'Casglu lleol a chasglu yn y siop','Upgrade to PRO &mdash; 99 EUR' => 'Uwchraddio i PRO - 99 EUR','Fluid Checkout PRO – Bundle' => 'Hylif Checkout PRO - Bwndel','All PRO features + All add-ons for a special price.' => 'Holl nodweddion PRO + Pob ychwanegiad am bris arbennig.','The bundle includes all add-ons we currently offer and Fluid Checkout add-ons we launch in the future.' => 'Mae&#39;r bwndel yn cynnwys yr holl ychwanegion rydyn ni&#39;n eu cynnig ar hyn o bryd ac ychwanegion Fluid Checkout rydyn ni&#39;n eu lansio yn y dyfodol.','226 EUR value (Save 42%)' => 'Gwerth 226 EUR (Arbed 42%)','Google Address Autocomplete' => 'Cyfeiriad Google Autocomplete','Address Book' => 'Llyfr Cyfeiriadau','EU-VAT Assistant' => 'Cynorthwy-ydd UE-TAW','All future add-ons *' => 'Pob ychwanegiad yn y dyfodol *','* For as long as you have an active subscription.' => '* Cyhyd â bod gennych danysgrifiad gweithredol.','Get the Bundle – Only 129 EUR' => 'Cael y Bwndel - Dim ond 129 EUR','All prices shown in EUR. If there are any divergencies with the prices on our website, the offers shown on the website superseed these and will be applied.' => 'Dangosir yr holl brisiau yn EUR. Os oes unrhyw wahaniaethau gyda&#39;r prisiau ar ein gwefan, mae&#39;r cynigion a ddangosir ar y wefan yn disodli&#39;r rhain a byddant yn cael eu cymhwyso.','Add-ons' => 'Ychwanegion','Enhance your checkout experience with these add-ons.' => 'Gwella&#39;ch profiad desg dalu gyda&#39;r ychwanegion hyn.','I already have it – Hide this offer' => 'Mae gen i eisoes - Cuddiwch y cynnig hwn','Installed &mdash; Activate' => 'Wedi&#39;i osod - Activate','Activated' => 'Wedi&#39;i actifadu','Up to 40% less checkout fields to fill in.' => 'Hyd at 40% yn llai o feysydd talu i&#39;w llenwi.','Avoid delivery delays and unsatisfied customers. Collect the <strong>correct address information</strong> from the first time they buy with you.' => 'Osgoi oedi wrth ddosbarthu a chwsmeriaid anfodlon. Casglwch y <strong>wybodaeth cyfeiriad cywir</strong> o&#39;r tro cyntaf y byddant yn prynu gyda chi.','Get this add-on &mdash; 29 EUR' => 'Mynnwch yr ychwanegyn hwn - 29 EUR','Address book' => 'Llyfr cyfeiriadau','Multiple saved addresses for shipping and billing.' => 'Cyfeiriadau lluosog wedi&#39;u cadw ar gyfer cludo a bilio.','Let customers <strong>save multiple shipping and billing addresses</strong> on their account and choose which ones to use at checkout and cart pages.' => 'Gadael i gwsmeriaid <strong>arbed sawl cyfeiriad cludo a bilio</strong> ar eu cyfrif a dewis pa rai i&#39;w defnyddio ar dudalennau til a throl.','Get this add-on &mdash; 59 EUR' => 'Mynnwch yr ychwanegyn hwn - 59 EUR','Simplified EU-VAT validation for your store.' => 'Dilysiad UE-TAW symlach ar gyfer eich siop.','Collect and <strong>validate EU VAT numbers at the checkout page</strong>, removes tax charges on reverse charge basis and confirms customer location when needed.' => 'Casglu a <strong>dilysu rhifau TAW yr UE ar y dudalen ddesg dalu</strong> , yn dileu taliadau treth ar sail gwrth-dâl ac yn cadarnhau lleoliad y cwsmer pan fo angen.','Get this add-on &mdash; 39 EUR' => 'Mynnwch yr ychwanegiad hwn - 39 EUR','All add-ons are sold separately and require the <strong>Fluid Checkout Lite</strong> plugin to be installed and activated, except when noted.' => 'Mae&#39;r holl ychwanegion yn cael eu gwerthu ar wahân ac mae angen gosod yr ategyn <strong>Fluid Checkout Lite</strong> a&#39;i actifadu, ac eithrio pan gaiff ei nodi.','Select an image' => 'Dewiswch ddelwedd','No image selected.' => 'Dim delwedd wedi&#39;i dewis.','Remove image' => 'Dileu delwedd','<a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">Log in to your account</a> to get your license key, or <a href="%s" target="_blank">purchase a new license key</a>.' => '<a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">Mewngofnodwch i&#39;ch cyfrif</a> i gael allwedd eich trwydded, neu <a href="%s" target="_blank">prynwch allwedd trwydded newydd</a> .','Valid until %s.' => 'Yn ddilys tan %s.','Expired on %s.' => 'Wedi dod i ben ar %s.','<a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">Log in to your account</a> to renew your license key and continue to receive updates and support.' => '<a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">Mewngofnodwch i&#39;ch cyfrif</a> i adnewyddu allwedd eich trwydded a pharhau i dderbyn diweddariadau a chefnogaeth.','License key cancelled.' => 'Allwedd trwydded wedi&#39;i chanslo.','<a href="%s" target="_blank">Purchase a new license key</a> and continue to receive updates and support.' => '<a href="%s" target="_blank">Prynu allwedd trwydded newydd</a> a pharhau i dderbyn diweddariadau a chefnogaeth.','Error: ' => 'Gwall: ','Setup & Documentation' => 'Gosod a Dogfennaeth','Great! Your checkout page is now running on Fluid Checkout.' => 'Gwych! Mae eich tudalen ddesg dalu bellach yn rhedeg ar Hylif Desg.','Here are a few resources for you to get started:' => 'Dyma ychydig o adnoddau i chi ddechrau arni:','Read the installation guide <a href="%s" target="_blank">Getting stated with Fluid Checkout</a>.' => 'Darllenwch y canllaw gosod <a href="%s" target="_blank">Cael datgan gyda Hylif Checkout</a> .','Setup layout and design on the <a href="%s">checkout options</a>.' => 'Gosod gosodiad a dyluniad ar yr <a href="%s">opsiynau desg dalu</a> .','Check if there are any <a href="%s">integration options</a> available for other plugins you have installed.' => 'Gwiriwch a oes unrhyw <a href="%s">opsiynau integreiddio</a> ar gael ar gyfer ategion eraill rydych chi wedi&#39;u gosod.','Visit <a href="%s" target="_blank">our documentation</a> for more information about Fluid Checkout features.' => 'Ewch <a href="%s" target="_blank">i&#39;n dogfennaeth</a> am ragor o wybodaeth am nodweddion Hylif Desg.','If you ever need help, <a href="%s" target="_blank">open a support ticket</a> on our official support channel.' => 'Os oes angen help arnoch chi erioed, <a href="%s" target="_blank">agorwch docyn cymorth</a> ar ein sianel gymorth swyddogol.','Cart layout' => 'Cynllun cart','Cart optimizations' => 'Optimeiddio cart','Enable cart page optimizations' => 'Galluogi optimeiddio tudalennau cart','Display the cart page with a layout similar to the checkout page.' => 'Dangoswch dudalen y drol gyda chynllun tebyg i&#39;r dudalen ddesg dalu.','Header and footer' => 'Pennawd a throedyn','Header and footer template' => 'Templed pennyn a throedyn','Controls whether to use the distraction free page header and footer or keep the currently active theme\'s header and footer.' => 'Yn rheoli a ddylid defnyddio pennyn a throedyn y dudalen sy&#39;n rhydd rhag tynnu sylw neu gadw pennyn a throedyn y thema sy&#39;n weithredol ar hyn o bryd.','Distraction free header and footer' => 'Pennawd a throedyn heb dynnu sylw','Theme\'s header and footer' => 'Pennawd a throedyn y thema','Cart elements' => 'Elfennau cart','Make the order summary stay visible on the cart page while scrolling' => 'Gwnewch i grynodeb y gorchymyn aros yn weladwy ar dudalen y drol wrth sgrolio','Coupon codes' => 'Codau cwpon','Select position where to display the coupon codes section on the cart page. Only applicable when AJAX cart and the integrated coupon codes in the checkout page are enabled.' => 'Dewiswch safle lle i arddangos yr adran codau cwpon ar dudalen y drol. Dim ond yn berthnasol pan fydd trol AJAX a&#39;r codau cwpon integredig yn y dudalen ddesg dalu wedi&#39;u galluogi.','Hidden' => 'Cudd','Before the cart items section' => 'Cyn yr adran eitemau cart','Inside the cart items section' => 'Y tu mewn i&#39;r adran eitemau cart','After the cart items section' => 'Ar ôl yr adran eitemau cart','Before the shipping section' => 'Cyn yr adran llongau','After the shipping section' => 'Ar ôl yr adran llongau','Before the order summary' => 'Cyn crynodeb y gorchymyn','Inside the order summary' => 'Y tu mewn i grynodeb y gorchymyn','Before the order totals' => 'Cyn i gyfanswm y gorchymyn','After the order totals' => 'Ar ôl y cyfansymiau archeb','After the order summary' => 'Ar ôl crynodeb y gorchymyn','Shipping' => 'Llongau','Select position where to display the shipping costs and calculator on the cart page.' => 'Dewiswch leoliad lle i arddangos y costau cludo a&#39;r gyfrifiannell ar dudalen y drol.','Display as a cart section' => 'Arddangos fel adran drol','Cross-sells' => 'Traws-werthu','Select position where to display the cross-sells section on the cart page.' => 'Dewiswch leoliad lle i arddangos yr adran traws-werthu ar dudalen y drol.','Before the cart actions' => 'Cyn i&#39;r drol weithredu','After the cart actions' => 'Ar ôl y camau cart','Layout of cross-sell items on the cart page.' => 'Cynllun traws-werthu eitemau ar dudalen y drol.','Optimized horizontal cross-sells layout' => 'Cynllun traws-werthu llorweddol wedi&#39;i optimeiddio','Theme\'s cross-sells layout' => 'Mae cynllun traws-werthu Thema','Number of cross-sell items to display on the cart page' => 'Nifer yr eitemau traws-werthu i&#39;w harddangos ar dudalen y drol','Trust symbols &amp; badges' => 'Symbolau a bathodynnau ymddiriedaeth','Add widget areas to the cart page' => 'Ychwanegu ardaloedd teclyn i dudalen y drol','These widget areas are used to add trust symbols and trust badges on the cart page.' => 'Defnyddir yr ardaloedd teclyn hyn i ychwanegu symbolau ymddiriedaeth a bathodynnau ymddiriedaeth ar dudalen y drol.','Checkout' => 'Desg dalu','Layout &amp; design' => 'Cynllun a dyluniad','Checkout layout' => 'Cynllun desg dalu','Design template' => 'Templed dylunio','General styles for the checkout steps, order summary and other sections. Might also apply to other pages such as the Cart, Order Received and View Order pages.' => 'Arddulliau cyffredinol ar gyfer y camau til, crynodeb archeb ac adrannau eraill. Gallai hefyd fod yn berthnasol i dudalennau eraill fel y tudalennau Cert, Archeb a Dderbynnir a Gweld Archeb.','Dark mode' => 'Modd tywyll','Enable dark mode' => 'Galluogi modd tywyll','Header and footer templates' => 'Templedi pennyn a throedyn','We recommend using the distraction free header and footer to avoid distractions at the checkout page. <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/cart-abandonment" target="_blank">Read the research about cart abandonment</a>.' => 'Rydym yn argymell defnyddio&#39;r pennyn a&#39;r troedyn heb unrhyw wrthdyniadau i osgoi unrhyw wrthdyniadau ar y dudalen ddesg dalu. <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/cart-abandonment" target="_blank">Darllenwch yr ymchwil am adael cert</a> .','Logo image' => 'Delwedd logo','Choose an image to be displayed on the checkout page header. Only applies when using the distraction free header and footer.' => 'Dewiswch ddelwedd i&#39;w harddangos ar bennyn y dudalen ddesg dalu. Dim ond wrth ddefnyddio&#39;r pennyn a&#39;r troedyn heb dynnu sylw y mae&#39;n berthnasol.','Header background color' => 'Lliw cefndir y pennawd','Choose a background color for the checkout page header. Only applies when using the distraction free header and footer.' => 'Dewiswch liw cefndir ar gyfer pennyn y dudalen ddesg dalu. Dim ond wrth ddefnyddio&#39;r pennyn a&#39;r troedyn heb dynnu sylw y mae&#39;n berthnasol.','HTML color value. ie: #f3f3f3' => 'Gwerth lliw HTML. hy: #f3f3f3','Page background color' => 'Lliw cefndir y dudalen','Choose a background color for the checkout page. Color is applied to the <em>body</em> element.' => 'Dewiswch liw cefndir ar gyfer y dudalen ddesg dalu. Mae lliw yn cael ei gymhwyso i elfen y <em>corff</em> .','Footer background color' => 'Lliw cefndir y troedyn','Choose a background color for the checkout page footer. Only applies when using the distraction free header and footer.' => 'Dewiswch liw cefndir ar gyfer troedyn y dudalen ddesg dalu. Dim ond wrth ddefnyddio&#39;r pennyn a&#39;r troedyn heb dynnu sylw y mae&#39;n berthnasol.','Checkout elements' => 'Elfennau desg dalu','Progress bar' => 'Bar cynnydd','Display the checkout progress bar when using multi-step checkout layout' => 'Dangoswch y bar cynnydd desg dalu wrth ddefnyddio cynllun desg dalu aml-gam','Make the checkout progress bar stay visible while scrolling' => 'Gwnewch i&#39;r bar cynnydd til aros yn weladwy wrth sgrolio','Express checkout' => 'Desg dalu cyflym','Enable the express checkout section' => 'Galluogi&#39;r adran desg dalu cyflym','Displays the express checkout section at checkout when supported payment gateways have this feature enabled.' => 'Yn dangos yr adran desg dalu cyflym wrth y ddesg dalu pan fydd y nodwedd hon wedi&#39;i galluogi gan byrth talu â chymorth.','Display express checkout buttons in one line for larger screens' => 'Arddangos botymau desg dalu cyflym mewn un llinell ar gyfer sgriniau mwy','Ignore additional checkout required fields when paying with a compatible express checkout payment gateway' => 'Anwybyddwch feysydd talu ychwanegol wrth dalu gyda phorth talu desg dalu cyflym cydnaws','Make the order summary stay visible while scrolling' => 'Gwnewch i grynodeb y gorchymyn aros yn weladwy wrth sgrolio','Choose a background color for the order summary section.' => 'Dewiswch liw cefndir ar gyfer yr adran crynodeb archeb.','Highlight the order totals row in the order summary table' => 'Amlygwch y rhes cyfansymiau trefn yn y tabl crynodeb trefn','Most useful when the order summary section does not have a highlighted background color. Might also apply to the Cart, Order Received and View Order pages when using Fluid Checkout PRO.' => 'Yn fwyaf defnyddiol pan nad oes gan yr adran crynodeb trefn liw cefndir wedi&#39;i amlygu. Gallai hefyd fod yn berthnasol i&#39;r tudalennau Cert, Archeb a Dderbynnir a Gweld Archeb wrth ddefnyddio Fluid Checkout PRO.','Action link on the order summary at checkout.' => 'Dolen gweithredu ar grynodeb yr archeb wrth y ddesg dalu.','Edit cart link' => 'Golygu dolen cart','Cart items count' => 'Mae eitemau cart yn cyfrif','Link to shop page' => 'Dolen i dudalen siop','Cart items' => 'Eitemau cert','Enable options to edit cart items on the checkout page' => 'Galluogi opsiynau i olygu eitemau cert ar y dudalen ddesg dalu','Allow customers to change product quantities or removing items directly at the checkout page.' => 'Caniatáu i gwsmeriaid newid meintiau cynnyrch neu dynnu eitemau yn uniongyrchol ar y dudalen ddesg dalu.','Hide cart items errors at the checkout page' => 'Cuddio gwallau eitemau cart ar y dudalen ddesg dalu','Do not display the cart items errors message at the top of the checkout page. When submitting the checkout form to complete the purchase, these error messages will always be displayed.'